afterTooltip: Minimum number of access before caching an object
authTokenTooltip: opaque string or JWT authorization token
autoDeletedTooltip: Auto delete queue when set to 'on', when there are no consumers
brokersTooltip: Comma separated list of Kafka broker addresses
certAuthorityTooltip: Path to certificate chain of the target NATS server
clientCertKeyTooltip: Client cert key for mTLS authentication
clientCertNatsTooltip: Client cert for NATS mTLS auth
clientKeyTooltip: Client cert key for NATS mTLS auth
clientTLSCertTooltip: Path to client certificate for mTLS auth
clientTLSKeyTooltip: Path to client key for mTLS auth
commentTooltip: You can add a comment to this setting
configURLTooltip: Config URL for Client ID configuration
corednsPathTooltip: Shared bucket DNS records, default is "/skydns"
deliveryMethodTooltip: Set to '1' for non-persistent or '2' for persistent queue
drivesTooltip: Mountpoints e.g. "/optane1" or "/optane2", you can write one per field
durableTooltip: Persist queue across broker restarts when set to 'on', default is 'off'
endpointsTooltip: List of etcd endpoints e.g. "http://localhost:2379", you can write one per field
excludeTooltip: Wildcard exclusion patterns e.g. "bucket/*.tmp" or "*.exe", you can write one per field
expiryTooltip: Cache expiry duration in days e.g. "90"
extensionsTooltip: Extensions to compress e.g. ".txt",".log" or ".csv", you can write one per field
formatTooltip: 'namespace' reflects current bucket/object list and 'access' reflects a journal of object operations, defaults to 'namespace'
groupNameAttributeTooltip: Search attribute for group name e.g. "cn"
indexTooltip: Elasticsearch index to store/update events, index is auto-created
internalTooltip: Set to 'on' for exchange to be not used directly by publishers, but only when bound to other exchanges
keepAliveTooltip: Keep-alive interval for MQTT connections in s,m,h,d
keyTooltip: Redis key to store/update events, key is auto-created
mandatoryTooltip: Quietly ignore undelivered messages when set to 'off', default is 'on'
mimeTypesTooltip: Mime types e.g. "text/*","application/json" or "application/xml", you can write one per field
name: Name
nameErr: Please verify that string is uppercase only and contains valid characters (numbers, dashes & underscores).
noWaitTooltip: Non-blocking message delivery when set to 'on', default is 'off'
pathPrefixTooltip: namespace prefix to isolate tenants e.g. "customer1/"
pingIntervalTooltip: Client ping commands interval in s,m,h,d. Disabled by default
qosTooltip: Set the quality of service priority, defaults to '0'
queueDirTooltip: staging dir for undelivered messages e.g. '/home/events'
queueLimitTooltip: maximum limit for undelivered messages, defaults to '10000'
quotaTooltip: Limit cache drive usage in percentage e.g. "90"
reconnectIntervalTooltip: Reconnect interval for MQTT connections in s,m,h,d
saslPasswordTooltip: Password for SASL/PLAIN or SASL/SCRAM authentication
saslTooltip: Set to 'on' to enable SASL authentication
saslUsernameTooltip: Username for SASL/PLAIN or SASL/SCRAM authentication
serverInsecureTooltip: Allow plain text connection to AD/LDAP server, defaults to "off"
serverLocationTooltip: Name of the location of the server e.g. "us-west-rack2"
streamingAsyncTooltip: Set to 'on', to enable asynchronous publish
streamingClusterIDTooltip: Unique ID for NATS streaming cluster
streamingMaxPublish: Streaming max publish ACKS in flight
streamingMaxPublishTooltip: Number of messages to publish without waiting for ACKs
streamingTooltip: Set to 'on', to use streaming NATS server
stsExpiryTooltip: temporary credentials validity duration in s,m,h,d. Default is "1h"
subject: Subject
tableNameTooltip: DB table name to store/update events, table is auto-created
tierInfoRetrievalErr: There was an error retrieving tier information
tlsClientAuthTooltip: Client Auth determines the Kafka server's policy for TLS client auth
tlsSkipVerifyLdapTooltip: Trust server TLS without verification, defaults to "off" (verify)
tlsSkipVerifyTooltip: Trust server TLS without verification, defaults to "on" (verify)
topicKafkaTooltip: Kafka topic used for bucket notifications
topicMqttTooltip: name of the MQTT topic to publish
urlElasticTooltip: Elasticsearch server's address, with optional authentication info
usernameFormatTooltip: List of username bind DNs e.g. "uid=%s","cn=accounts","dc=myldapserver" or "dc=com", you can write one per field
usernameSearchBaseTooltip: List of username search DNs, you can write one per field
usernameSearchFilterTooltip: User search filter, for example "(cn=%s)" or "(sAMAccountName=%s)" or "(uid=%s)"
versionTooltip: Specify the version of the Kafka cluster e.g '2.2.0'
